    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h2>DTRSmartClient</h2><div><p>This statement defines the expected capabilities of systems wishing to conform to the ''DTR SMART on FHIR Client'' role.  Systems conformant to this IG Capability Statement <strong>SHALL</strong> also serve as a SMART on FHIR client.</p>\n</div><table><tr><td>Mode</td><td>CLIENT</td></tr><tr><td>Description</td><td><div><p>A DTR SMART on FHIR Client provides an application conforming to the SMART on FHIR specification and related requirements declared in this Implementation Guide.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td>Transaction</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>System History</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>System Search</td><td></td></tr></table><table><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">Read</b></th><th><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">Search</b></th><th><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">Update</b></th><th><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">Create</b></th></tr><tr><td>Coverage</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-coverage-r4.html\">DTR Coverage R4</a></td><td></td><td>y</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>DeviceRequest</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-devicerequest.html\">DTR Device Request</a></td><td></td><td></td><td>y</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>MedicationRequest</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-medicationrequest.html\">DTR Medication Request</a></td><td></td><td></td><td>y</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>NutritionOrder</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-nutritionorder.html\">DTR Nutrition Order</a></td><td></td><td></td><td>y</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ServiceRequest</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-servicerequest.html\">DTR Service Request</a></td><td></td><td></td><td>y</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Parameters</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-parameters.html\">DTR Operation Parameters</a></td><td>y</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Questionnaire</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-sdc-questionnaire.html\">DTR SDC Questionnaire</a><br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-sdc-questionnaire-adapt.html\">DTR SDC Questionnaire for adaptive form</a></td><td>y</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>QuestionnaireResponse</td><td>Supported profiles:<br/>\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"StructureDefinition-dtr-questionnaireresponse-r4.html\">DTR Questionnaire Response R4</a></td><td>y</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></table></div>"
